Annotation1.Text: Whenever In1 becomes ACTIVE, then In2 shall become INACTIVE after a delay of 5 steps.

Annotation2.Text: Whenever In becomes true, it shall stay true for the following 3 steps as well.

Annotation3.Text: Whenever In3 is ON and In4 is less that THRESHOLD, then In3 shall become OFF within 5 steps.

Annotation4.Text:
After Sensor is detected at HIGH for 7 consecutive steps, Cmd becomes and stays true for 
the remaining duration of the Sensor value HIGH unless manual reset is detected.

Annotation1.Text:
node detector_fixedDetector(u, reset:bool; w, d, r:int)

returns(out:bool);

var cnt: int;

A, detected:bool;

let

cnt = 0 -> if (pre cnt < w) then

if (u and not reset) then pre cnt + 1

else 0

else if ((pre cnt < d or pre cnt < r) and pre detected and not reset)

then pre cnt + 1

else if (u and not reset) then 1 else 0;

detected = false -> if (pre cnt < w)

then (u and not reset)

else if ((pre cnt < d or pre cnt < r) and pre detected and not reset)

then pre detected

else u and not reset;

A = false -> pre detected and not reset;

out = false -> (pre cnt >= w) and (pre cnt >= d ) and (pre cnt < r) and A;

node detector_consecDetector(u, reset:bool; w:int)

returns(out:bool);

var cnt:int;

let

cnt = 0 -> if u and not reset

then if (pre cnt >= w) then pre cnt

else pre cnt + 1

else 0;

out = false -> u and not reset and (pre cnt >= w) ;
